<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤٦)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَبَّادُ بنُ عَمْرٍو التَّغْلِبِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - هَلَّا سَأَلْتَ بَنِي السَّفَّاحِ هَلْ سَعِدُوا ... بِأَمْرِهِمْ إِنَّ غِبَّ الْبَغْيِ خَوَّانُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ - مَا وَرَّثَ الْبَغْيُ قَوْمًا غَيْرَهُمْ رَشَدًا ... بَلْ يَهْلِكُونَ بهِ وَالدَّهْرُ أَلْوَانُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤٧)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَال صَالِحُ بنُ عَبْدِ الْقُدُّوسِ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - وَمَا غَنِمَ الْعَادِي عَلَى النَّاسِ ظَالِمًا ... وَلا خَابَ مَظْلُومٌ عَفا حِينَ يُظلَمُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤٨)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ طَرَفَةُ بنُ الْعَبْدِ الْبَكْرِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الكامل)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - الظُّلْمُ فَرّقَ بَيْنَ حَيَّيْ وَائِل ... بَكْرٌ تسَاقِيهَا الْمَنَايَا تَغْلِبُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢ - قَدْ يُورِدُ الظُّلْمُ الْمُبَيَّنُ آجِنًا ... مِلْحًا يُخَالَطُ بالذُّعَافِ وَيُقْشَبُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤٩)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ جَوَّاسُ بنُ الْقَعْطَلِ:</span> <span class="c2">(الكامل)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>